CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 15, 1955, pg. 32, reads: "Publicity Head - Lenny Levy, ex-Pittsburgh Pirate catcher and present Buc scout, who operates the Forbes Field Auto Sales, Inc., is handling publicity for the NIADA convention. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Former Pittsburgh Pirates baseball player Lenny Levy seated at desk in Forbes Field Auto Sales, with DeSoto advertisement in background
